    <section id="apply" class="pt-5">
        <p class="h1 shrink gradient-text" style="font-size: 70px;">1.0 How it Works</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="h4 gradient-text">1.1 <b>Applying</b></p>
        <p>
        Create an account and experience the convenience of being able to apply for jobs online. BookMeDental is a job offering website focusing in the field of dentistry, dedicated to providing various job opportunities to upcoming applicants.
        </p>

        <ol type="a">
          <li><i>What happens when you apply as an Applicant?</i></li> <br>
          <p>As you apply as an Applicant, you will gain access to search and apply for any job in the field of dentistry based on the position you have applied for. </p>

          <li><i>What happens when you apply as an Employer?</i></li> <br>
          <p>As you apply as an Employer, you will gain access to the Websites features for hiring an applicant to be a (parttime/fulltime) employee. </p>

        </ol>
    </section>

    <section id="hire" class="pt-5">
        <hr>
        <p class="h4 gradient-text">1.2 <b>Hiring</b></p>
        <ol type="a">
          <li><i>How does the Employer hire an employee?</i></li> <br>
          <p>Employers can hire potential employees either via a job posting created, or via quick hire. Through job posting, Employers will be able to view a list of applicants that have applied for the job created, as well as download and view their resumes for further deliberation.</p>

          <li><i>How will the Applicant be informed that they got hired?</i></li> <br>
          <p>Applicants will be notified by the app when they have been hired or contacted by the employer. BookMeDental will notify applicants through email for any activity (i.e. hiring notification, or contact notification) </p>

          <li><i>What does it mean to be hired Temporarily in this Application?</i></li> <br>
          <p>Being hired temporarily means that applicants will be working for a limited period of time for a specific employer. This also means that the temporary employee’s wage will be per hour basis instead of a fixed rate (for permanent employees) </p>

          <li><i>What is the difference between getting hired Temporarily and Permanently?</i></li> <br>
          <p>The difference between getting hired Temporarily and Permanently is that temporary workers will only work for the employer for a specified period of time, with their wage being per hour. Permanent workers... </p>
    </section>

    <section id="network" class="pt-5">
        <hr>
        <p class="h4 gradient-text">1.3 <b>Networking</b></p>
        <p>
        Expand your network and discover different employment opportunities created by different employers.
        </p>

        <ol type="a">
          <li><i>What will applying a clinic to the website mean?</i></li> <br>
          <p>Registering a clinic to the website means that you are looking for potential employees for your clinic, and would need more manpower either temporarily or permanently. </p>

          <li><i>What is the relationship between Employer and Applicant in the website?</i></li> <br>
          <p>BookMeDental allows applicants to connect with employers through job offerings, and increase the hiring opportunities that applicants can receive. At the same time, BookMeDental connects the employers to other applicants, giving them a various amount of potential employees to hire. </p>
        </ol>
    </section>

    <section id="explore" class="pt-5">
        <hr>
        <p class="h4 gradient-text">1.4 <b>Explore</b></p>
        <p>
        Explore every feature that is available to you.
        </p>

        <ol type="a">
          <li><i>What are the features used by Employers?</i></li> <br>
          <p>BookMeDental provides different sets of features to different users based on their registration type, and allows the users to explore further. For users that registered as employers, you have access to the list of applicants that have registered to BookMeDental, where you can hire them for work. You can also create job offerings that applicants can apply for. Lastly, if you’re looking for potential employees on short notice, you can contact applicants immediately. You can also update your dashboard information, as well as your job postings. </p>

          <li><i>What are the features used by Applicants?</i></li> <br>
          <p>BookMeDental provides different sets of features to different users based on their registration type, and allows the users to explore further. For users that registered as applicants, you have access to searching and applying for job offerings posted by employers in BookMeDental. You can also update your dashboard information, as well as the resume you have uploaded to provide better and up-to-date information. </p>
        </ol>

     <img src="imgs/gfx/h2.png" style="width: inherit; max-width: 650px; display:block;  margin: 0 auto;">
